structure.unit: RELIGIOUS, CHARITABLE, AND EDUCATIONAL SOCIETIES -- NONSTOCK, NONPROFIT CORPORATIONS

law.history: Repealed 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 165, sec. 70. -- Created 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 133, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Nonstock, nonprofit corporations authorized; who may incorporate; purposes; exclusions; religious, charitable or educational corporation; application of other statutes; no tax exemption.
